Solve This Proof State:

Hypotheses:


Goal:
forall m : fmap, inv_hmap m -> inj_dart (succf m) (F m)

Premises:
Inductive fmap : Set := V : fmap | I : fmap -> dart -> tag -> point -> fmap | L : fmap -> dim -> dart -> dart -> fmap
F = fun (m : fmap) (z : dart) => A_1 m one (A_1 m zero z) : fmap -> dart -> dart
inv_hmap = fix inv_hmap (m : fmap) : Prop := match m with | V => True | I m0 x _ _ => inv_hmap m0 /\ prec_I m0 x | L m0 k0 x y => inv_hmap m0 /\ prec_L m0 k0 x y end : fmap -> Prop
inj_dart = fun (Df : dart -> Prop) (f : dart -> dart) => forall x x' : dart, Df x -> Df x' -> f x = f x' -> x = x' : (dart -> Prop) -> (dart -> dart) -> Prop Argument scopes are [function_scope function_scope]
succf = fun (m : fmap) (z : dart) => pred m zero z /\ pred m one (A_1 m zero z) : fmap -> dart -> Prop
MA0.bij_f_1 : forall m : fmap, inv_hmap m -> bij_dart (exd m) (McA0.f_1 m)
McA0.bij_f_1 : forall m : fmap, inv_hmap m -> bij_dart (exd m) (cA_1 m Md0.k)
inj_cA : forall (m : fmap) (k : dim), inv_hmap m -> inj_dart (exd m) (cA m k)
inj_cA_1 : forall (m : fmap) (k : dim), inv_hmap m -> inj_dart (exd m) (cA_1 m k)
F_1_F : forall (m : fmap) (z : dart), inv_hmap m -> exd m z -> exd m (F m z) -> F_1 m (F m z) = z
nd_card : forall m : fmap, ndN m = card (fmap_to_set m)
succf_exd_F : forall (m : fmap) (z : dart), inv_hmap m -> succf m z -> exd m (F m z)
not_exd_nil : forall m : fmap, inv_hmap m -> ~ exd m nil
F_nil : forall m : fmap, inv_hmap m -> F m nil = nil
inj_A_1 : forall (m : fmap) (k : dim), inv_hmap m -> inj_dart (pred m k) (A_1 m k)
inj_A : forall (m : fmap) (k : dim), inv_hmap m -> inj_dart (succ m k) (A m k)
MA0.incls_orbit : forall (m : fmap) (x : dart), inv_hmap m -> exd m x -> incls (MA0.Iter_orb m x) (fmap_to_set m)
MA0.incls_rem : forall (m : fmap) (x : dart), inv_hmap m -> exd m x -> incls (MA0.Iter_rem m x) (fmap_to_set m)
MA1.incls_orbit : forall (m : fmap) (x : dart), inv_hmap m -> exd m x -> incls (MA1.Iter_orb m x) (fmap_to_set m)
MA0.Iter_f_Si : forall (m : fmap) (i : nat) (z : dart), inv_hmap m -> exd m z -> Iter (MA0.f m) (S i) z = Iter (MA0.f m) i (MA0.f m z)
MA1.Iter_f_Si : forall (m : fmap) (i : nat) (z : dart), inv_hmap m -> exd m z -> Iter (MA1.f m) (S i) z = Iter (MA1.f m) i (MA1.f m z)
MA0.degree_per : forall (m : fmap) (z : dart), inv_hmap m -> exd m z -> Iter (MA0.f m) (MA0.degree m z) z = z
MA0.Iter_plus_inv : forall (m : fmap) (z : dart) (p i : nat), inv_hmap m -> exd m z -> Iter (MA0.f m) p z = z -> Iter (MA0.f m) (p + i) z = Iter (MA0.f m) i z
MA1.Iter_plus_inv : forall (m : fmap) (z : dart) (p i : nat), inv_hmap m -> exd m z -> Iter (MA1.f m) p z = z -> Iter (MA1.f m) (p + i) z = Iter (MA1.f m) i z
MA1.Iter_plus : forall (m : fmap) (z : dart) (p i : nat), inv_hmap m -> exd m z -> Iter (MA1.f m) (p + i) z = Iter (MA1.f m) i z -> Iter (MA1.f m) p z = z
inj_neq : forall n m : nat, neq n m -> Zne (Z.of_nat n) (Z.of_nat m)
MA0.Iter_mult : forall (m : fmap) (z : dart) (n p : nat), inv_hmap m -> exd m z -> Iter (MA0.f m) p z = z -> Iter (MA0.f m) (n * p) z = z
MA0.exd_Iter_f_1 : forall (m : fmap) (n : nat) (z : dart), inv_hmap m -> exd m z < -> exd m (Iter (MA0.f_1 m) n z)
MA1.exd_Iter_f : forall (m : fmap) (n : nat) (z : dart), inv_hmap m -> exd m z < -> exd m (Iter (MA1.f m) n z)
MA0.Iter_plus_mult : forall (m : fmap) (z : dart) (n p i : nat), inv_hmap m -> exd m z -> Iter (MA0.f m) p z = z -> Iter (MA0.f m) (i + n * p) z = Iter (MA0.f m) i z
Zne_left : forall n m : Z, Zne n m -> Zne (n + - m) 0
MA1.ex_i_upb : forall (m : fmap) (z : dart), inv_hmap m -> exd m z -> let nr := MA1.Iter_upb m z in {i : nat | (i < nr)%nat /\ Iter (MA1.f m) i z = Iter (MA1.f m) nr z}
MA1.Iter_period : forall (m : fmap) (z : dart) (i n : nat), inv_hmap m -> exd m z -> let p := MA1.Iter_upb m z in Iter (MA1.f m) (i + n * p) z = Iter (MA1.f m) i z
MA1.unicity_mod_p : forall (m : fmap) (z : dart) (j k : nat), inv_hmap m -> exd m z -> let p := MA1.Iter_upb m z in (j < p)%nat -> (k < p)%nat -> Iter (MA1.f m) j z = Iter (MA1.f m) k z -> j = k
MA1.mod_p : forall (m : fmap) (z : dart) (i : nat), inv_hmap m -> exd m z -> let p := MA1.Iter_upb m z in {j : nat | Iter (MA1.f m) i z = Iter (MA1.f m) j z /\ (j < p)%nat}
